#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.fmod.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.fmod"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:1 of
msgid "Return the element-wise remainder of division."
msgstr "返回逐元素的除法余数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:3 of
#, python-format
msgid ""
"This is the NumPy implementation of the C library function fmod, the "
"remainder has the same sign as the dividend `x1`. It is equivalent to the"
" Matlab(TM) ``rem`` function and should not be confused with the Python "
"modulus operator ``x1 % x2``."
msgstr ""
"这是 C 库函数 fmod 的 NumPy 实现，余数与被除数 `x1` 具有相同的符号。它"
"等价于 Matlab(TM) 的 ``rem`` 函数，不应与 Python 的模运算符 ``x1 % x2`` "
"混淆。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:8 of
msgid "Dividend."
msgstr "被除数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:10 of
msgid "Divisor."
msgstr "除数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:12 of
msgid ""
"A location into which the result is stored. If provided, it must have a "
"shape that the inputs broadcast to. If not provided or `None`, a freshly-"
"allocated tensor is returned. A tuple (possible only as a keyword "
"argument) must have length equal to the number of outputs."
msgstr ""
"用于存储结果的位置。如果提供了该参数，则其形状必须能够广播到输入形状。"
"如果未提供或为 `None`，则返回一个新分配的张量。元组（只能作为关键字参数）"
"的长度必须等于输出数量。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:17 of
msgid ""
"Values of True indicate to calculate the ufunc at that position, values "
"of False indicate to leave the value in the output alone."
msgstr "值为 True 表示在该位置计算 ufunc，值为 False 表示保留输出中的值不变。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:20 of
msgid ""
"For other keyword-only arguments, see the :ref:`ufunc docs "
"<ufuncs.kwargs>`."
msgstr "对于其他仅关键字参数，请参见 :ref:`ufunc 文档 <ufuncs.kwargs>`。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod of
msgid "返回"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:23 of
msgid "**y** -- The remainder of the division of `x1` by `x2`."
msgstr "**y** -- `x1` 除以 `x2` 的余数。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:28 of
msgid ":py:obj:`remainder`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:29 of
msgid "Equivalent to the Python ``%`` operator."
msgstr "等价于 Python 的 ``%`` 运算符。"

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:31 of
msgid ":py:obj:`divide`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:34 of
msgid "备注"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.arithmetic.fmod.fmod:35 of
msgid ""
"The result of the modulo operation for negative dividend and divisors is "
"bound by conventions. For `fmod`, the sign of result is the sign of the "
"dividend, while for `remainder` the sign of the result is the sign of the"
" divisor. The `fmod` function is equivalent to the Matlab(TM) ``rem`` "
"function."
msgstr ""
"对于负数被除数和除数，模运算的结果遵循约定。对于 `fmod`，结果的符号与"
"被除数相同，而对于 `remainder`，结果的符号与除数相同。`fmod` 函数等价于 "
"Matlab(TM) 的 ``rem`` 函数。"

